Second Department,

February, 1951 *

(February 19, 1951) In the Matter of the Construction of the Will of William A. Milleg, Deceased. Mary R. Milleg, Appellant; Isabel Goodwin et al., Respondents.

Not published with other decisions of February 19, 1951, 278 App. Div. 664, April 27, 1953, 281 App. Div. 991, and Jan. 27, 1958, 5 A D 2d 789.— [Rep.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted upon consent, without costs, and appeal dismissed, without costs. Present—Carswell, Acting P. J., Johnston, Adel, Wenzel and MacCrate, JJ.
